{"tid":1553201,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"感謝各位前線。冇你地，我可能打唔到依段野。","createTime":"2019-09-08T14:01:36.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-08T23:55:48.000Z","uid":247640,"like":67,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"c5ff0138573fbc30940481d5cc7f60d8ca2aaebd","tid":1553201,"uid":247640,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T14:01:36.000Z","msg":"今日3點半去到遮打花園，<br />\n開始跟住人群行。<br />\n因為人好多，行得好慢，<br />\n行到4點半個時，其實都未上到美領，<br />\n已經開始聽到話中環站封左有狗。<br />\n<br />\n因為後面都係人，所以都要繼續向前行，<br />\n繼續叫口號，繼續撚狗。<br />\n大概5點9行返落黎地面，<br />\n就話碼頭、中環站、金鐘站都係狗，<br />\n要經銅鑼灣走。<br />\n我跟住人群行，無啦啦聽到「跑啊」<br />\n回頭一望，見到有幾隻防暴狗衝緊落黎。<br />\n我唔知有幾多隻，<br />\n因為我見到之後已經盡快跑，<br />\n費事塞住後面。<br />\n跑左一段路，大家就話可以轉急步行，<br />\n唔好受傷。<br />\n<br />\n途中，一個應該係高中既妹妹，<br />\n好驚咁黎問我係咪依個方向去銅鑼灣。<br />\n我話係，一齊行。<br />\n其實我心入面都好驚，黑警乜都做得出。<br />\n你又封撚晒d站，要我地走去邊？<br />\n<br />\n大概行到去金鐘/灣仔中間，<br />\n我見到好多著晒裝既前線，<br />\n準備緊set路障，<br />\n係咁叫我地依班冇裝備既人快d走。<br />\n個一刻，我真係好想喊，<br />\n除左同佢地講「加油！小心」<br />\n我唔知我可以做咩。<br />\n<br />\n感謝你地背起左保護市民既負任，<br />\n你地大可以走先唔洗理我地後面冇裝既人，<br />\n但你地選擇留低拖住，爭取時間俾我地走先。<br />\n如果冇你地，我今日可能已經返唔到屋企。<br />\n希望你地每一個都可以平安返到屋企，<br />\n核爆都唔割！<br />\n<br />\n五大訴求，缺一不可！<br />\n黑警死全家！<br />\nSorry for 1999. <br />\n我依家心情都平伏唔到，一路打一路喊。"},{"pid":"2317bcab82d6f1b3ae73dadafc39483fa6cfcd91","tid":1553201,"uid":189582,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T14:05:29.000Z","msg":"完全明白，相信有去過現場都好大感受！<br />\n勇武多謝你地<br />\n放核彈都唔割！"},{"pid":"15e6e48f66911975cd6a2f388a1c00992e8ae400","tid":1553201,"uid":80684,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T14:08:10.000Z","msg":"多謝前線同咁多位勇武<br />\n唔好信d鬼話我地割蓆<br />\n<br />\n我地香港人 一直都係同一班人<br />\n前線又好 和理非又好<br />\n我地都係一家人<br />\n多謝你地<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e86757a7ec791e73df17e4ba9c641acf758ba19b","tid":1553201,"uid":272587,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T14:09:18.000Z","msg":"勇武巴絲 希望你地唔好比啲分化post呃到 現場既人一定唔會怪你地 一定知咩事 唔好因為冷氣豪子而分化和勇 我愛你地<br />\np仔懇求大家幫幫手入啲屌前線既po度不推文地淨化翻個po！辛苦前線 多謝前線！"},{"pid":"ad2895dd22c0d1fc47d4a7c4fb24a5e254334741","tid":1553201,"uid":187185,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T14:09:23.000Z","msg":"感謝前線!"},{"pid":"3da60d8e9a523d645dd4d81b1a73f265396b510d","tid":1553201,"uid":67168,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T14:09:28.000Z","msg":"多謝勇武手足<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"773a4f04cb325440da8e33a97c1ad737b43d2b8f","tid":1553201,"uid":217990,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T14:09:55.000Z","msg":"絕對感謝前線手足"},{"pid":"0fb84f00359d17247a936f4402b05818f2936777","tid":1553201,"uid":80684,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T14:10:20.000Z","msg":"再推 多謝前線每一位手足<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9363cc7a719fe093822021bf8041efc711c2fc0a","tid":1553201,"uid":34213,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T14:11:18.000Z","msg":"見到手足響馬路邊上Gear<br />\n多謝你地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"36e3b26517e907584c6e5269e819ab365fd855a9","tid":1553201,"uid":139294,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T14:11:30.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"b5645d411b403af38a535254da9852fae18d710a","tid":1553201,"uid":301237,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T14:12:15.000Z","msg":"感謝前線 唔好比人分化到"},{"pid":"1f7a82b5f9c75e5ccbf28268a5537b7428a3f157","tid":1553201,"uid":17381,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T14:14:30.000Z","msg":"大家自己睇今晚d警察點執法<br />\n亂拉路人<br />\n黑警濫捕可恥"},{"pid":"f9d1c8916561785176f1c1aa68d17f9d622b19f1","tid":1553201,"uid":28355,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T14:15:30.000Z","msg":"前線手足先係保護香港市民安全<br />\n狗=黑社會=危害市民生命財產"},{"pid":"3d14c1c9992021aed9fe56b3fb9c3d37ffa0f7d7","tid":1553201,"uid":215556,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T14:16:14.000Z","msg":"支持"},{"pid":"0bd161c8d17897513afd8a8218048f010fc6f9ca","tid":1553201,"uid":247640,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T14:19:02.000Z","msg":"所謂既香港警察，<br />\n先係對市民最大威脅。<br />\n頭先我見到d狗，真係好撚驚，<br />\n好撚驚佢地會衝上黎追住我地。<br />\n係班前線勇武保護我地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e3cf33ef7399adc527ba0767e6817648cf4d39b0","tid":1553201,"uid":299467,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T14:20:28.000Z","msg":"多謝各位手足保護我地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b9677a342571512c896474e55b81aeeaeaad5da0","tid":1553201,"uid":175731,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T14:21:57.000Z","msg":"呢d好文要多推，5毛分化唔洗理"},{"pid":"0942cf31b569d214ed914d988d43176646687810","tid":1553201,"uid":129016,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T14:22:46.000Z","msg":"勇武手足<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e81db43d22aaca388bd36515e6080e0120e8f7e5","tid":1553201,"uid":295872,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T14:29:23.000Z","msg":"我今日都係單拖在場，唔係勇武既話，有好多好似我呢啲咩裝備都無既人，已經坐左係新屋嶺。<br />\n<br />\n前線，我唔知點樣可以多謝你地。但真係好感謝你地，用條命黎保護我地。"},{"pid":"05227e64fe8b03d9714660ad1aabee63599ab407","tid":1553201,"uid":206021,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T14:57:31.000Z","msg":"多謝前線 我愛你地<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6ae37b11ea57d71779021e277c7c94ba31e99b5a","tid":1553201,"uid":273071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T15:11:48.000Z","msg":"多謝勇武！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e5218d160f781f0e5d8d3b22da9f80ac12283d31","tid":1553201,"uid":312855,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T15:50:57.000Z","msg":"多謝勇武<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"14b27613d2ca4d42789b757b811412d801f00ff3","tid":1553201,"uid":10933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T23:49:52.000Z","msg":"多謝前線勇武！"},{"pid":"0f855bdb8a09934c2e834c9cb85f65bbf7ccfb42","tid":1553201,"uid":268217,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T23:55:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />多謝前線"}]}